To implement these changes, I will transform the application into a static presentation page. The interactive 3D game logic will be removed from `App.tsx` and replaced with a layout featuring the descriptive text of Zaira and an interactive "Black Card" that generates a visualization using the `gemini-2.5-flash-image` model.

I will update `services/geminiService.ts` to handle image generation instead of text memories.

# Updated files:

## services/geminiService.ts

Updated to use `gemini-2.5-flash-image` for generating the city illustration.

```typescript
import { GoogleGenAI, Modality } from "@google/genai";

const apiKey = process.env.API_KEY || '';
const ai = new GoogleGenAI({ apiKey });

export const generateCityIllustration = async (): Promise<string | null> => {
  if (!apiKey) {
    console.error("No API Key found");
    return null;
  }

  const prompt = `
    A high-quality axonometric etching of the invisible city of Zaira. 
    M.C. Escher style architecture with impossible stairs, arches, and vaults.
    Black ink on paper, cross-hatching texture, detailed linework.
    The buildings are interconnected in complex, paradoxical ways.
    The atmosphere is nostalgic, ancient, and surreal.
    White background, distinct black lines.
  `;

  try {
    const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
      model: 'gemini-2.5-flash-image',
      contents: {
        parts: [{ text: prompt }],
      },
      config: {
        responseModalities: [Modality.IMAGE],
      }
    });

    const part = response.candidates?.[0]?.content?.parts?.[0];
    if (part && part.inlineData) {
      return `data:${part.inlineData.mimeType};base64,${part.inlineData.data}`;
    }
    return null;
  } catch (error) {
    console.error("Error generating illustration:", error);
    return null;
  }
};
```

## App.tsx

Completely rewritten to act as a static page with the Black Card interaction.

```tsx
import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { generateCityIllustration } from './services/geminiService';
import { Loader2 } from 'lucide-react';

const App: React.FC = () => {
  const [imageUrl, setImageUrl] = useState<string | null>(null);
  const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false);
  const [hasAttempted, setHasAttempted] = useState(false);

  const handleReveal = async () => {
    if (imageUrl || isLoading) return;

    setIsLoading(true);
    setHasAttempted(true);
    const url = await generateCityIllustration();
    if (url) {
      setImageUrl(url);
    }
    setIsLoading(false);
  };

  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 md:p-16 bg-[#fdf6e3] text-[#2c2c2c] relative overflow-y-auto">
      {/* Background Texture Overlay */}
      <div className="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-10 z-0" 
           style={{backgroundImage: 'url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\'100\' height=\'100\' viewBox=\'0 0 100 100\' xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%3E%3Cpath d=\'M11 18c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm48 25c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7z\' fill=\'%23000000\' fill-opacity=\'0.1\' fill-rule=\'evenodd\'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")'}}
      ></div>

      <main className="max-w-3xl w-full z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-12">

        {/* Header */}
        <header className="space-y-4 animate-fadeIn">
          <h1 className="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-display tracking-widest text-[#1a1a1a]">ZAIRA</h1>
          <div className="h-1 w-24 bg-[#1a1a1a] mx-auto"></div>
          <p className="text-sm font-serif tracking-widest uppercase text-[#555]">The City of High Bastions</p>
        </header>

        {/* Descriptive Text */}
        <section className="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-[#3a3a3a] italic max-w-2xl">
          <p>
            "A description of Zaira as it is today should contain all Zaira’s past. 
            The city, however, does not tell its past, but contains it like the lines of a hand, 
            written in the corners of the streets, the gratings of the windows, the banisters of the steps, 
            the antennae of the lightning rods, the poles of the flags, every segment marked in turn 
            with scratches, indentations, scrolls."
          </p>
        </section>

        {/* The Black Card */}
        <div 
          onClick={handleReveal}
          className={`
            relative w-full max-w-md aspect-square 
            bg-[#1a1a1a] shadow-2xl cursor-pointer 
            transition-all duration-1000 ease-in-out transform
            ${imageUrl ? 'hover:scale-[1.02]' : 'hover:scale-[0.98]'}
            group overflow-hidden border-4 border-[#1a1a1a]
          `}
        >
          {/* Image Layer */}
          {imageUrl && (
            <img 
              src={imageUrl} 
              alt="Etching of Zaira" 
              className="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0 animate-fadeIn transition-opacity duration-1000"
              style={{ opacity: 1, filter: 'sepia(20%) contrast(110%)' }}
            />
          )}

          {/* Loading / Placeholder Layer */}
          <div className={`
            absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-[#fdf6e3]
            transition-opacity duration-700
            ${imageUrl ? 'opacity-0 pointer-events-none' : 'opacity-100'}
          `}>
            {isLoading ? (
              <div className="flex flex-col items-center space-y-4">
                <Loader2 className="animate-spin h-12 w-12 opacity-80" />
                <span className="font-display tracking-widest text-sm opacity-80 animate-pulse">Constructing Memory...</span>
              </div>
            ) : (
              <div className="flex flex-col items-center space-y-2 group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
                <span className="font-display text-2xl tracking-widest border-b border-[#fdf6e3] pb-1">REVEAL</span>
                <span className="font-serif italic text-sm opacity-60">Touch to see the city</span>
              </div>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Footer Quote */}
        <footer className="font-serif text-[#666] text-lg max-w-xl">
          <p>
            The city soaks it up like a sponge and expands. 
            It consists of relationships between the measurements of its space and the events of its past.
          </p>
        </footer>

      </main>
    </div>
  );
};

export default App;
```

To implement the requested changes, I will redesign the layout to remove the sidebar and introduce a responsive top navigation bar. The content will be centered, and the quote will be moved to a footer section.

